          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1581674378057-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1581674378057-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your<strong> cucumber </strong>into discs</p><p>Slice each individual<strong> cucumber disc</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop the root[s] off your<strong> lettuce </strong>and separate the <strong>leaves</strong>, then wash and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1581674382327-x200.jpg",
