            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and juice of your <strong>lime[s]</strong> with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your<strong> lime dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1581674397813-x200.jpg",
